# ============================================
# Streaming-JP - Japan Streaming Supplement
# ============================================
# Strategy Group: Streaming-JP
# Purpose: Supplemental Japan streaming rules not covered by individual service files
# Coverage: U-NEXT, FOD, TVer, dTV, Lemino, NHK+, Paravi, Disney+ JP,
#           Rakuten TV, GYAO, Telasa, J:COM On Demand, etc.
# Node Requirement: JP node with clean IP (recommended: Flower JP Premium2)
# Note: Use alongside Netflix.list, Abema TV.list, DMM.list, Niconico.list, etc.
# ============================================

# ========================================
# U-NEXT
# ========================================

